{
  "stem": "13382.5",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So then we went through by train through Linz, which was the border of the Russian zone.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And again, some sort of force and some bribery, so we got through.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we got to Salzburg, which was a military accommodation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] we stayed there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I'm just going-- so from there on, we went over the border from-- from Austria to-- to Vienna, to Freilassing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That was very close to Berchtesgaden and-- and that area.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It's beautiful aesthetically.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And-- and-- and geologically-- it was-- I mean, you know, up in the mountains.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And there was a DP camp again, so we stayed, which was called Ainring.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the next stop from there was go through Austria and Germany.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We went to Belgium.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Because in Belgium, there was the headquarters of-- of the Jewish brigade, which was formed by the British.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And the Jewish Brigade was really, mainly-- all of the ex-Jewish brigades was involved in this Bricha.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Belgium, there was a castle and an estate where the Bricha-- where the Jewish brigade had previously.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they accommodated us there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we stayed about seven months there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was quite very pleasant, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Was there fore-- Obviously, have to find-- I mean, there was not--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First of all, you had to be able to get through all this-- these [? ring. ?] And second, you have to have passage through the-- across the sea, or sailing.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, they didn't have-- we couldn't go with a normal, sort of a sailing arrangement.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they had to buy first some sort of old junk and convert it to something.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, accrue it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that-- that takes, really, time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And all to do in, sort of, without the British knowing about it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think they did, but-- finished?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We're--",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
